What you will learn:

Using FlexBox to Layout an Oracle JET application

How to use this sample:

1. Discuss CSS3 and FlexBox.

2. Usage of "oj-flex".

3. Usage of "oj-flex-item".

4. Point out how easy it is to use FlexBox in Oracle JET applications.

5. Show the related page on the Oracle JET site:

http://www.oracle.com/webfolder/technetwork/jet/uiComponents-flex-basics.html

6. All the code changes are in index.html.